{
  "stem": "3380.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now why did tanneries came in my mind?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we used to burn part of the leather.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we could smell the same, the same smell-- skin, you know, like burning of skin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I thought, I think that this will be a good place for us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I thought to myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when they opened up the doors and they start screaming and hollering, and with whips, like [GERMAN], you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Within five minute, you from normal people, they become animals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't even know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't-- we didn't care what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to put us-- chased us out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they separate out the male from the female.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then this, we start making selections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if this was Mengele's.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know that was a, an officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was going with a motorcycle, came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked-- we had to be undressed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, no, we did not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were not undressed, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The male separate and the woman were separated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he ask, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what is your profession?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Naturally, I told him that I am a tanner [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm 20 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That time, I was 20 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, he pointed to the side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to go to the right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know, because on the left, when they had the, the sick people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I know that this goes in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this goes on a different direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have seen one episode while the selection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One was called in that he should go to the left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he try-- as to go to the left, he tried to run into the right.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the SS pushed him back with the guns.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
